ISLAMABAD, Jul 28 (APP):The Royal Court said in a statement on Sunday that Prince Abdullah bin Khalid bin Turki bin Abdulaziz bin Turki Al Saud had passed away.
According to Saudi Press Agency (SPA) the funeral prayer will be performed today, Sunday, 28/07/2024, after the Isha prayer at the Grand Mosque in Makkah.
